Do you remember?

1334
01:19:09.995 --> 01:19:11.080
Miss.

1335
01:19:11.789 --> 01:19:13.249
Who the hell are you?

1336
01:19:16.252 --> 01:19:18.212
Aki. don't be scared.

1337
01:19:20.214 --> 01:19:21.298
Don't be scared.

1338
01:19:21.382 --> 01:19:24.760
Miss. you can't just grab me like that.

1339
01:19:25.636 --> 01:19:28.013
What are you doing in our house? Rekrek?

1340
01:19:29.265 --> 01:19:30.432
Rekrek?

1341
01:19:32.101 --> 01:19:33.269
Who is this?

1342
01:19:45.406 --> 01:19:46.782
Chill out. bro.

1343
01:19:48.075 --> 01:19:49.368
She's a visitor.

1344
01:20:34.747 --> 01:20:36.040
<i>I don't know.</i>

1345
01:20:39.126 --> 01:20:41.462
<i>I thought I was just forgetful.</i>

1346
01:20:46.216 --> 01:20:48.135
<i>I thought it was the stress.</i>

1347
01:20:56.935 --> 01:20:58.937
But I was already sick.

1348
01:21:01.982 --> 01:21:04.777
After several examinations.

1349
01:21:05.778 --> 01:21:07.237
we have found thatâ€¦

1350
01:21:08.530 --> 01:21:11.158
You have early-onset Alzheimer's Disease.

1351
01:21:11.742 --> 01:21:12.742
What?

1352
01:21:15.037 --> 01:21:16.246
<i>Now. in your case.</i>

1353
01:21:16.330 --> 01:21:18.374
<i>there might be rapid deterioration</i>

1354
01:21:18.457 --> 01:21:20.501
<i>because you have
a high level of education.</i>

1355
01:21:21.502 --> 01:21:23.337
I'm hungry. Let's eat.

1356
01:21:23.420 --> 01:21:24.963
I'm still fixing thisâ€¦

1357
01:21:25.047 --> 01:21:26.507
- It's a camera!
- Camera.

1358
01:21:26.590 --> 01:21:28.008
- Camcorder.
- Camcorder. yeah.

1359
01:21:28.092 --> 01:21:29.218
You old man.

1360
01:21:29.301 --> 01:21:31.595
<i>The things you mentioned.</i>

1361
01:21:31.678 --> 01:21:35.015
<i>when you forget
the words for certain things.</i>

1362
01:21:35.599 --> 01:21:38.018
<i>forgetting certain eventsâ€¦
Those are symptoms.</i>

1363
01:21:38.102 --> 01:21:38.977
You were absent yesterday.

1364
01:21:39.061 --> 01:21:39.895
<i>We missed you.</i>

1365
01:21:39.978 --> 01:21:40.896
<i>Did we have class yesterday?</i>

1366
01:21:40.979 --> 01:21:43.857
<i>You're so funny. Why are you in uniform?</i>

1367
01:21:43.941 --> 01:21:46.026
Why else? For work.

1368
01:21:46.110 --> 01:21:47.277
It's Sunday.

1369
01:21:47.361 --> 01:21:48.570
<i>Oh. love.</i>

1370
01:21:48.654 --> 01:21:49.654
<i>Happy birthday!</i>

1371
01:21:49.696 --> 01:21:52.741
See? If I didn't point it out.
you wouldn't greet me.

1372
01:21:52.825 --> 01:21:54.785
<i>Our electric bill's not paid yet?</i>

1373
01:21:54.868 --> 01:21:56.286
This is a disconnection notice.

1374
01:21:56.370 --> 01:21:57.704
Love. I promise I'll do it.

1375
01:21:57.788 --> 01:22:00.165
<i>Why is this still here?
Is it still not paid?</i>

1376
01:22:01.417 --> 01:22:02.418
Am I supposed to do that?

1377
01:22:02.501 --> 01:22:03.669
<i>Have you seen my phone?</i>

1378
01:22:03.752 --> 01:22:05.629
You're looking for your phone

1379
01:22:05.712 --> 01:22:07.107
instead of going to my birthday dinner.

1380
01:22:07.131 --> 01:22:09.633
- Oh. fuck! That's right.
- Yeah?

1381
01:22:12.094 --> 01:22:16.181
<i>On November 26. 1896â€¦</i>

1382
01:22:20.519 --> 01:22:22.896
<i>Actually. I don't know what's happening.</i>

1383
01:22:23.605 --> 01:22:26.066
I don't know why I forget to go to class.

1384
01:22:26.150 --> 01:22:27.484
I don't know what's happening.

1385
01:22:27.568 --> 01:22:29.403
I don't know what's happening. ma'am.

1386
01:22:29.486 --> 01:22:31.071
Have you gotten a checkup?

1387
01:22:32.781 --> 01:22:35.284
<i>Tinola chicken mami. your favorite!</i>

1388
01:22:35.367 --> 01:22:36.869
Why is there no chicken?

1389
01:22:40.706 --> 01:22:42.332
<i>You ditched Fel!</i>

1390
01:22:42.416 --> 01:22:45.169
<i>They went out of their way
to help you get a job.</i>

1391
01:22:45.252 --> 01:22:47.212
<i>and you didn't even show up. Aki?</i>

1392
01:22:47.296 --> 01:22:49.590
That's been on your calender
for two months. remember?

1393
01:22:49.673 --> 01:22:50.673
What's wrong with you?

1394
01:22:52.968 --> 01:22:58.182
<i>Another symptom is forgetting
the purpose of certain objects.</i>

1395
01:23:01.268 --> 01:23:03.437
<i>Love. I need to tell you something.</i>

1396
01:23:04.021 --> 01:23:05.355
You didn't pick me up.

1397
01:23:07.399 --> 01:23:09.610
I couldn't pick you up becauseâ€¦

1398
01:23:14.114 --> 01:23:16.950
<i>I didn't know how to start the car.</i>

1399
01:23:17.034 --> 01:23:18.869
I don't know why.

1400
01:23:23.582 --> 01:23:25.250
I don't know why.

1401
01:23:28.879 --> 01:23:31.381
You have impulsive purchases.

1402
01:23:31.465 --> 01:23:33.258
Out of control spending.

1403
01:23:33.342 --> 01:23:37.346
These are all behaviors and symptoms
of someone with Alzheimer's Disease.

1404
01:23:37.429 --> 01:23:38.889
This is expensive.

1405
01:23:38.972 --> 01:23:41.058
<i>We can't even pay for the house.</i>

1406
01:23:41.141 --> 01:23:43.227
And you're buying all this shit?

1407
01:23:44.561 --> 01:23:46.480
<i>I startedâ€¦</i>

1408
01:23:47.898 --> 01:23:49.566
Drinking.

1409
01:23:49.650 --> 01:23:50.943
Alcohol.

1410
01:23:51.026 --> 01:23:52.694
<i>So that somehow.</i>

1411
01:23:53.779 --> 01:23:56.323
I could feel better.

1412
01:23:56.406 --> 01:23:58.825
Come on. I'll send you to rehab.
since you're an alcoholic!

1413
01:23:58.909 --> 01:24:00.077
I'm not an alcoholic!

1414
01:24:00.160 --> 01:24:01.912
Then what the fuck is this?

1415
01:24:01.995 --> 01:24:03.622
She thought I was an alcoholic.

1416
01:24:04.373 --> 01:24:05.791
Forget about all this. okay?

1417
01:24:05.874 --> 01:24:07.084
Forget about me. Aki.

1418
01:24:07.167 --> 01:24:08.544
Let's go.

1419
01:24:08.627 --> 01:24:10.212
Pia!

1420
01:24:12.047 --> 01:24:13.924
<i>I didn't tell her.</i>

1421
01:24:16.635 --> 01:24:18.178
<i>I don't know.</i>

1422
01:24:18.262 --> 01:24:20.389
<i>All I know is</i>

1423
01:24:20.472 --> 01:24:22.099
<i>something was wrong.</i>

1424
01:24:23.600 --> 01:24:25.227
<i>Where am I?</i>

1425
01:24:26.520 --> 01:24:27.980
<i>What is this place?</i>

1426
01:24:36.321 --> 01:24:38.031
<i>I didn't want to drag her into it.</i>

1427
01:24:40.784 --> 01:24:42.327
<i>Iâ€¦</i>

1428
01:24:44.788 --> 01:24:46.999
<i>I didn't want to be a burden to her.</i>

1429
01:24:47.791 --> 01:24:48.959
<i>Untilâ€¦</i>

1430
01:24:53.755 --> 01:24:55.007
<i>She left.</i>

1431
01:25:04.016 --> 01:25:06.393
<i>I never wanted this. To forget.</i>

1432
01:25:10.272 --> 01:25:12.399
<i>But she forgot about me.</i>

1433
01:25:18.989 --> 01:25:22.618
<i>She forgot about everything
we shared together.</i>

1434
01:25:24.953 --> 01:25:26.830
<i>But I can't blame her.</i>

1435
01:25:27.831 --> 01:25:29.082
<i>She didn't know.</i>

1436
01:25:30.626 --> 01:25:33.378
<i>It must be tiring to take care of me.</i>

1437
01:25:36.423 --> 01:25:39.885
<i>But if she knew.
I know she wouldn't leave me.</i>

1438
01:25:43.221 --> 01:25:44.765
<i>She loves me.</i>

1439
01:25:46.808 --> 01:25:48.393
<i>She loves me so much.</i>

1440
01:26:24.471 --> 01:26:26.264
We didn't know

1441
01:26:26.348 --> 01:26:30.143
when it started. It all happened so fast.

1442
01:26:30.227 --> 01:26:31.436
And that was it.

1443
01:26:31.520 --> 01:26:33.939
All his memories were gone.

1444
01:26:34.022 --> 01:26:36.858
Maybe he got it from my brother.

1445
01:26:36.942 --> 01:26:38.318
Aki's father.

1446
01:26:38.402 --> 01:26:43.156
In Aki's case. I am very sorry to tell you

1447
01:26:43.240 --> 01:26:45.242
that in the late stage of Alzheimer's.

1448
01:26:45.325 --> 01:26:46.827
in this situation.

1449
01:26:46.910 --> 01:26:51.248
he's going to need
round-the-clock assistance and care.

1450
01:26:52.666 --> 01:26:55.335
Doc. won't he be able
to remember anything?

1451
01:26:56.211 --> 01:26:59.297
Sometimes. he would be able
to remember some things.

1452
01:26:59.381 --> 01:27:00.507
For example.

1453
01:27:00.590 --> 01:27:03.927
he could remember his old hobbies.

1454
01:27:04.010 --> 01:27:04.845
Likeâ€¦

1455
01:27:04.928 --> 01:27:07.514
Like playing a certain musical instrument.

1456
01:27:08.432 --> 01:27:11.393
But in his case right now.

1457
01:27:12.185 --> 01:27:15.564
it will be hard for him
to remember things.

1458
01:27:16.481 --> 01:27:18.775
Maybe there are treatments abroad?

1459
01:27:19.359 --> 01:27:21.903
Just to help him remember even a little.

1460
01:27:23.739 --> 01:27:25.824
Even just to recognize me.

1461
01:27:26.366 --> 01:27:28.952
I'm sorry. There's none.

1462
01:27:39.129 --> 01:27:40.380
What will you do. dear?

1463
01:27:40.922 --> 01:27:42.841
You still have work in Singapore.

1464
01:27:45.260 --> 01:27:47.345
I think I'm going
to stay here for a while. Ma.

1465
01:27:48.889 --> 01:27:50.390
For Aki.

1466
01:27:52.017 --> 01:27:54.895
Sis. do you want us
to take care of Aki for a bit?

1467
01:27:55.479 --> 01:27:58.148
As much as possible.
I want to be the one taking care of him

1468
01:27:58.231 --> 01:27:59.231
That's whyâ€¦

1469
01:27:59.566 --> 01:28:02.778
I'm going to resign
from my job in Singapore.

1470
01:28:02.861 --> 01:28:03.861
Dear.

1471
01:28:08.200 --> 01:28:10.202
Stay strong. okay?

1472
01:28:11.453 --> 01:28:13.413
Take good care of Aki.

1473
01:28:18.585 --> 01:28:20.462
We're here for you.

1474
01:28:23.882 --> 01:28:24.901
Come on. This will be quick.

1475
01:28:24.925 --> 01:28:25.842
- No.
- Come on.

1476
01:28:25.926 --> 01:28:26.760
Look at me.

1477
01:28:26.843 --> 01:28:27.969
- No.
- This will be quick.

1478
01:28:28.053 --> 01:28:30.096
- Take off your clothes.
- I don't want to.

1479
01:28:32.849 --> 01:28:34.017
Shit.

1480
01:28:34.768 --> 01:28:35.936
Oh no! Oh my God!

1481
01:28:36.978 --> 01:28:37.979
What do I do?

1482
01:28:39.564 --> 01:28:40.774
- Oh no! Pia!
- Rekrek!

1483
01:28:40.857 --> 01:28:42.001
- What happened?
- Rekrek. I'm sorry.

1484
01:28:42.025 --> 01:28:43.568
I was trying to give Aki a bath.

1485
01:28:43.652 --> 01:28:44.694
I forgot.

1486
01:28:44.778 --> 01:28:45.946
Are you hurt?

1487
01:28:46.029 --> 01:28:47.489
N-no.

1488
01:28:50.200 --> 01:28:51.201
Aki!

1489
01:28:53.036 --> 01:28:54.162
Oh no!

1490
01:28:54.246 --> 01:28:57.415
Aki. what did you do?

1491
01:28:57.499 --> 01:28:58.583
You're so clumsy.

1492
01:28:58.667 --> 01:29:00.919
Rek. can you clean that up?

1493
01:29:01.002 --> 01:29:02.337
There's more over there.

1494
01:29:02.420 --> 01:29:03.421
Aki.

1495
01:29:03.505 --> 01:29:04.589
Oh! Oh!

1496
01:29:04.673 --> 01:29:06.508
Oh no! Aki. Aki.

1497
01:29:06.591 --> 01:29:07.735
Aki. come here. I'll give you a bath.

1498
01:29:07.759 --> 01:29:09.320
- Come on. so you can get cleaned up.
- No.

1499
01:29:09.344 --> 01:29:11.096
- I don't want to.
- Come on. Please. Aki.

1500
01:29:11.179 --> 01:29:12.406
- I'll help you.
- I said I don't want to!

1501
01:29:12.430 --> 01:29:13.598
- What?
- Hey!

1502
01:29:14.641 --> 01:29:16.226
Who are you. miss?

1503
01:29:16.309 --> 01:29:18.228
What are you doing in my house?

1504
01:29:19.271 --> 01:29:21.648
I'm not kidding. I'll call the police!

1505
01:29:21.731 --> 01:29:22.649
Who are you?

1506
01:29:22.732 --> 01:29:23.817
Who are you?

1507
01:29:24.401 --> 01:29:26.695
Aki. Aki. it's me. Pia.

1508
01:29:26.778 --> 01:29:28.321
I don't know you!

1509
01:29:29.072 --> 01:29:30.323
Who are you?

1510
01:29:31.324 --> 01:29:32.409
Rekrek. who is this?

1511
01:29:32.492 --> 01:29:33.785
Get out! I'm not kidding!

1512
01:29:33.869 --> 01:29:35.662
Please. I don't want any trouble!

1513
01:29:35.745 --> 01:29:38.164
Bro. calm down. Calm down.

1514
01:29:39.291 --> 01:29:41.293
This is trespassing. miss.
I'm not kidding.

1515
01:29:41.376 --> 01:29:42.669
This is trespassing!

1516
01:29:43.169 --> 01:29:45.797
Calm down. Get in there. bro.

1517
01:29:47.674 --> 01:29:49.009
Stay there. okay?

1518
01:29:50.010 --> 01:29:52.178
Go on. Rek. I'll take care of this.

1519
01:29:54.848 --> 01:29:56.641
Aki. here. Come on.

1520
01:29:56.725 --> 01:29:58.184
Just a little more.

1521
01:29:58.268 --> 01:29:59.728
Come on.

1522
01:29:59.811 --> 01:30:01.521
Aki. come on.

1523
01:30:04.274 --> 01:30:06.693
Aki. it's not good to waste food. okay?

1524
01:30:06.776 --> 01:30:08.129
Why do you keep telling me to eat?

1525
01:30:08.153 --> 01:30:10.196
You're so annoying.
You're like a broken record.

1526
01:30:10.280 --> 01:30:11.656
Look. you made a mess.

1527
01:30:11.740 --> 01:30:13.092
Pia. here. For cleaning the wound.

1528
01:30:13.116 --> 01:30:14.116
Thank you.

1529
01:30:14.618 --> 01:30:15.535
I'll clean this up.

1530
01:30:15.619 --> 01:30:16.786
Thank you.

1531
01:30:16.870 --> 01:30:19.372
Get him a new bowl.

1532
01:30:22.542 --> 01:30:24.294
Rek. can you keep an eye on Aki?

1533
01:30:24.377 --> 01:30:26.921
I think someone's at the door.

1534
01:30:38.767 --> 01:30:39.851
Carlo.

1535
01:30:50.320 --> 01:30:51.529
- Carlo.
- Hey.

1536
01:30:51.613 --> 01:30:53.365
- Have some juice.
- Thank you.

1537
01:30:53.448 --> 01:30:54.448
Sure.

1538
01:31:00.955 --> 01:31:01.955
Oh?

1539
01:31:01.998 --> 01:31:02.998
What happened?

1540
01:31:03.958 --> 01:31:05.210
- Are you okay?
- Ah. this?

1541
01:31:05.293 --> 01:31:07.629
It's nothing. I slipped

1542
01:31:07.712 --> 01:31:09.756
Yeah. I'm so clumsy.

1543
01:31:10.840 --> 01:31:12.425
Ah. anyway.

1544
01:31:12.509 --> 01:31:14.260
I wanted to tell you

1545
01:31:14.344 --> 01:31:17.722
that I resigned
from the company in Singapore.

1546
01:31:17.806 --> 01:31:19.683
I'm going to start my own

1547
01:31:19.766 --> 01:31:22.268
Singapore-based digital agency.

1548
01:31:22.352 --> 01:31:23.395
Wow!

1549
01:31:23.478 --> 01:31:25.897
That's good. Congratulations.

1550
01:31:25.980 --> 01:31:26.856
Thank you.

1551
01:31:26.940 --> 01:31:30.276
I thought of offering you a position
in the company.

1552
01:31:30.360 --> 01:31:32.362
I want to make you VP.

1553
01:31:34.114 --> 01:31:35.240
Uhâ€¦

1554
01:31:36.157 --> 01:31:40.453
- Carlo. it's just that...
- Also. aside from being VP.

1555
01:31:40.537 --> 01:31:42.539
I want you to make a shareholder.

1556
01:31:43.415 --> 01:31:45.458
We'll be business partners. in a sense.

1557
01:31:45.542 --> 01:31:47.794
We'll both run the company.

1558
01:31:48.670 --> 01:31:51.881
And I'll give you a relocation package.

1559
01:31:51.965 --> 01:31:53.967
Uh. allowance.

1560
01:31:54.050 --> 01:31:55.677
Company car!

1561
01:31:55.760 --> 01:31:57.929
I'll even pay for your place there.

1562
01:31:58.596 --> 01:32:00.348
- And thenâ€¦ Maybe we could...
- Carlo.

1563
01:32:02.976 --> 01:32:03.976
Thank you.

1564
01:32:05.854 --> 01:32:07.188
Thank you for the offer.

1565
01:32:08.648 --> 01:32:10.817
But I don't think I can accept it.

1566
01:32:12.402 --> 01:32:14.070
But this is your dream. remember?

1567
01:32:14.154 --> 01:32:16.781
You were always
telling me about this back then.

1568
01:32:20.285 --> 01:32:21.411
Honestlyâ€¦

1569
01:32:22.078 --> 01:32:24.873
I thought that would make me happy.

1570
01:32:27.500 --> 01:32:28.835
But it turns out

1571
01:32:30.044 --> 01:32:31.796
that it's not what I need.

1572
01:32:33.256 --> 01:32:35.091
- Pia. please?
- Carlo.

1573
01:32:37.218 --> 01:32:39.012
Thank you so much for the offer.

1574
01:32:40.180 --> 01:32:42.182
but I have to respectfully decline.

1575
01:32:43.600 --> 01:32:45.185
Pia. please?

1576
01:32:46.144 --> 01:32:47.854
I don't know why. butâ€¦

1577
01:32:48.813 --> 01:32:50.148
I still love you.

1578
01:32:52.984 --> 01:32:54.194
Carlo. I'm sorry.

1579
01:32:56.362 --> 01:32:57.489
What the hell?

1580
01:32:57.572 --> 01:33:03.495
You need to finish your food. Calm down.

1581
01:33:03.578 --> 01:33:04.871
What are you doing?

1582
01:33:06.039 --> 01:33:07.957
One last bite.

1583
01:33:08.041 --> 01:33:09.167
No!

1584
01:33:13.630 --> 01:33:14.630
Leave me alone!

1585
01:33:15.215 --> 01:33:16.508
There you go.

1586
01:33:19.969 --> 01:33:21.262
Press this one.

1587
01:33:30.313 --> 01:33:32.524
Someone told me

1588
01:33:32.607 --> 01:33:34.359
that I used to be good
at playing the piano.

1589
01:33:35.652 --> 01:33:37.695
